HEADWORD: Haematoplastic
<hw>Haem`a*to*plas"tic</hw> <pr>(-pl⟦acr⟧s"t⟦icr⟧k)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Haemato-</ets> + <ets>-plastic</ets>.]</ety>
